Default value is 0 Example 1: Offset = 2 means Business Date of the dependee Stream/Process must be completed for, or after, the Business Date of the dependent (-s) Stream plus 2 days. Tag.name: TCF::BT Input Type
Tag.description:
The input source could be either Delta or Full Input:
- Delta: The source has only subset of current records. In this case, the input records will be compared and output rows only generated based on the inputs. - Full: The source has a complete set of current records. In this case, the input records will be compared and output rows will be generated based on the inputs and also based on existing current records in the target table missing from input.
